    {
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "chapterTitle": "五十六、《关于正确处理人民内部矛盾的问题》和整风反右（上）",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23640914_6_39783-39803",
          "range": "39783-39803",
          "rangeStart": 39783,
          "rangeEnd": 39803,
          "markText": "讲的第二个问题，是关于人民闹事如何处理。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709014507,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-02-27 14:15:07",
          "chapterUid": 6,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640914&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=39783&rangeEnd=39803",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e3e328b07168bb52e3e5f74?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=39783&rangeEnd=39803"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23640914_6_18185-18251",
          "range": "18185-18251",
          "rangeStart": 18185,
          "rangeEnd": 18251,
          "markText": "有人说外国的自由很好，我们这里自由很少。我说，没有抽象的自由，只有阶级的自由，具体的自由，抽象的、一般的自由，世界上就没有那个东西。",
          "colorStyle": 5,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709000882,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-02-27 10:28:02",
          "chapterUid": 6,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640914&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=18185&rangeEnd=18251",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e3e328b07168bb52e3e5f74?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=18185&rangeEnd=18251"
        }
      ]
